        Exclusion Criteria

        Co-existing Condition:

        Patients with the following symptoms or conditions are excluded:

        AIDS defining condition within 1 month of study entry.

        Prior Medication:

        Excluded:

        Patients with any history of antiretroviral therapy treatment.
      </textblock>
